        <abstract> 
<p>Thanks ES for his note [missing]. CD had understood that what was wanted was a eulogy [of Leopold von Buch] combined with historical criticism, after the French practice. Agrees that historico-critical sketches of work of great foreigners have a place in <hi rend="italic">Philosophical Transactions</hi> and wishes he had taste and capacity for it.</p> 
